''Wasn't satisfied till he made him a tail.
Made him a tail....''

605
01:10:53,960 --> 01:10:57,160
You see, Miss Celie,
you gots a beautiful smile.

606
01:10:59,400 --> 01:11:03,560
Well, Miss Celie, l do believe
it's time for me to go.

607
01:11:04,680 --> 01:11:09,160
September. Yeah, September be a
good time to go off in the world.

608
01:11:12,040 --> 01:11:13,640
What's the matter?

609
01:11:17,320 --> 01:11:19,560
He beat me when you ain't here.

610
01:11:21,240 --> 01:11:22,320
Who do?

611
01:11:23,880 --> 01:11:25,160
Albert?

612
01:11:26,760 --> 01:11:27,880
Mister.

613
01:11:31,240 --> 01:11:32,840
Why he do that?

614
01:11:44,360 --> 01:11:46,920
He beat me for not being you.

615
01:12:11,240 --> 01:12:13,160
l know he a bully...

616
01:12:14,440 --> 01:12:17,640
...but there's some things l love about him.

617
01:12:18,280 --> 01:12:19,880
You still love him?

618
01:12:20,200 --> 01:12:22,440
l got what you call a passion for him.

619
01:12:22,920 --> 01:12:26,920
lf l was ever going to have a husband,
he'd been it. But he weak.

620
01:12:27,400 --> 01:12:29,000
Tell me the truth.

621
01:12:29,480 --> 01:12:31,880
Do you mind if Albert sleep with me?

622
01:12:32,200 --> 01:12:33,960
You like sleeping with him?

623
01:12:34,280 --> 01:12:38,040
l have to confess, l love it. Don't you?

624
01:12:39,880 --> 01:12:42,760
No, most time l pretend l ain't even there.

625
01:12:43,080 --> 01:12:44,960
He don't know the difference.

626
01:12:45,160 --> 01:12:47,720
He don't never ask me how l feel.

627
01:12:48,040 --> 01:12:50,120
He never ask me about myself.

628
01:12:50,440 --> 01:12:53,160
He just climb on top of me
and do his business.

629
01:12:53,480 --> 01:12:55,720
''Do his business''?

630
01:12:56,040 --> 01:12:57,640
You sound like...

631
01:12:57,960 --> 01:13:00,840
...he going to the toilet on you.

632
01:13:01,480 --> 01:13:03,560
That's what it feel like.

633
01:13:06,600 --> 01:13:08,360
Then, Miss Celie...

634
01:13:09,960 --> 01:13:12,040
...that mean you still a virgin.

635
01:13:14,280 --> 01:13:17,800
-Yeah, because don't nobody love me.
-l love you.

636
01:13:18,120 --> 01:13:20,680
-You think l's ugly.
-No, l don't.

637
01:13:21,000 --> 01:13:24,200
''You ugly. You sure is ugly.''

638
01:13:26,160 --> 01:13:27,960
''You still ugly.''

639
01:13:29,320 --> 01:13:30,920
Amen.

640
01:13:32,040 --> 01:13:35,720
Oh, Miss Celie, that was just
the salt in the sugar.

641
01:13:36,040 --> 01:13:38,600
Me being jealous of you and Albert.

642
01:13:38,920 --> 01:13:41,000
l think you beautiful.

643
01:15:39,100 --> 01:15:41,020
Shug like honey...

644
01:15:41,340 --> 01:15:44,220
...and now, I'sjust like a bee.

645
01:15:44,540 --> 01:15:48,380
I's follow her everywhere,
want to go where she go.

646
01:15:49,340 --> 01:15:53,820
What life like for her?
And why she sometime get so sad?

647
01:15:54,300 --> 01:15:56,540
So sad,just like me.

648
01:16:01,700 --> 01:16:02,700
Hello.

649
01:16:11,580 --> 01:16:13,020
How you been?

650
01:16:17,340 --> 01:16:19,740
l been sick. Maybe you heard.

651
01:16:20,540 --> 01:16:24,540
But l feels better now.
l been staying with Albert and Celie.

652
01:16:26,140 --> 01:16:27,980
They been taking care of me.

653
01:16:35,300 --> 01:16:37,700
Place bring back memories.

654
01:16:39,460 --> 01:16:42,820
l used to stand right over there
watching you.

655
01:16:44,420 --> 01:16:46,340
Best preacher in the world.

656
01:16:47,460 --> 01:16:51,940
The way you'd make your voice
rise and fall when you turned a phrase.

657
01:16:53,740 --> 01:16:58,060
The way you looked in your blue suit.
Girls cutting their eyes at you.

658
01:16:58,340 --> 01:16:59,820
Something to see.

659
01:17:01,700 --> 01:17:04,740
You'd smile at us and say:

660
01:17:06,020 --> 01:17:07,300
''Ladies...

661
01:17:07,940 --> 01:17:11,460
''...God is trying to tell you something,
if you please.''

662
01:17:11,940 --> 01:17:13,700
And we sang.

663
01:17:14,020 --> 01:17:16,100
We sang our hearts out.

664
01:17:17,540 --> 01:17:20,540
''l couldn't sleep at night

665
01:17:25,860 --> 01:17:28,420
''And l was wondering why''

