671
01:18:27,180 --> 01:18:28,620
What you doing?

672
01:18:33,580 --> 01:18:34,700
Nothing.

673
01:18:35,700 --> 01:18:37,620
lt don't look like that to me.

674
01:18:40,620 --> 01:18:42,860
l need you to sit on my suitcase.

675
01:19:25,180 --> 01:19:26,380
On your way.

676
01:19:33,580 --> 01:19:35,820
There something you got to say?

677
01:19:39,340 --> 01:19:41,740
What's the matter? Cat got your tongue?

678
01:19:41,820 --> 01:19:43,100
Don't be scared.

679
01:19:50,740 --> 01:19:52,340
l's going to miss you.

680
01:19:54,780 --> 01:19:56,540
l's going to miss you, too.

681
01:19:56,660 --> 01:19:58,420
l'm going to miss you, too.

682
01:20:01,620 --> 01:20:03,060
Let's go!

683
